description:
Test your skills on your favorite Video Poker game.

A perfect game for all video poker fans who want to try different casino poker games and pay tables.

Video Poker Collection contains 15 poker machines in one:
* Aces and Eights
* Aces and Faces
* All American
* Black Jack Bonus Poker
* Bonus Poker
* Bonus Poker Deluxe
* Deuces and Joker Poker
* Deuces Wild
* Double Bonus Poker
* Jacks or Better
* Joker Poker
* Super Double Double Bonus Poker
* Tens or Better
* Two Ways Royal
* White Hot Aces

Features:
* Simple and clean design.
* Fast and easy game play.
* Gamble your winnings.
* View statistics.
* Climb the Leaderboard and earn bragging rights.
name: Video Poker Collection
